-HIGH-PROTEIN

review.reviewBody: Almost NO WORDS to describe the Summer-Berry Lemonade Starbucks Refreshers® Beverage!!!!!! It was flavourful and fresh but not too sweet. The pearl on bottom were fresh and just enough, we added fresh strawberries. Tired key, Provolone & Pesto on Ciabatta is a go to staple and works for my 5 year old to my 16 year old
Lattes very nicely made, everything arrived hot- i wouldve loved a napkin or two, chocolate croissants can get super messy.
I thought I ordered 3 large strawberry refreshers and it was the smallest cup
Bacon Bacon, Sausage & Egg Wrap is extremely mid - lacks bacon and sausage and egg and is mostly potato
